    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You run hundreds of scenarios in your head in a single moment, figuring out how to best deal with incoming damage. You gain +5 AC to the triggering attack or advantage on the triggering dexterity saving throw. Until the beginning of your next turn,all other attacks made against you have disadvantage and you have advantage on dexterity throws. Additionally, you gain an additional reaction which can only be used for the <em><strong>Read The Enemy</strong></em> reaction.</p><p></p>",
